2
00:00:00.270 --> 00:00:03.140
Open up the borderless map, then

3
00:00:03.140 --> 00:00:06.340
Head for that unknown edge of the ocean

4
00:00:06.340 --> 00:00:10.730
LET’S SAIL ON right now, hoist your sails up high

5
00:00:10.730 --> 00:00:13.720
Riding on the wind

6
00:00:18.850 --> 00:00:23.060
DON’T GIVE UP, it’s time to finish what we started

7
00:00:23.250 --> 00:00:26.030
So don't you grow disheartened

8
00:00:26.340 --> 00:00:29.790
Laugh the tears away through the storm

9
00:00:29.990 --> 00:00:34.220
SHOUT IT OUT, when you feel down always remember

10
00:00:34.560 --> 00:00:36.820
That’s what your friends are there for

11
00:00:36.850 --> 00:00:38.980
Y’know there’s no point in fronting,

12
00:00:38.980 --> 00:00:42.900
your crew will always have your back

13
00:00:43.270 --> 00:00:47.000
Even in the face of utter darkness

14
00:00:47.230 --> 00:00:49.990
C’mon, BRAVE IT OUT We’ll be alright

15
00:00:50.290 --> 00:00:53.780
Together you know that we’ll never lose a fight

16
00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:56.770
Open up the borderless map, then

17
00:00:56.790 --> 00:00:59.630
Head for that unknown edge of the ocean

18
00:00:59.930 --> 00:01:04.210
All great journeys starts with a single step

19
00:01:04.280 --> 00:01:05.220
DREAMIN’ ON

20
00:01:05.220 --> 00:01:08.000
Open up the borderless map, then

21
00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:10.740
Raise the flag we swore to defend

22
00:01:10.890 --> 00:01:13.630
We’ll never stop until we’ve reached the top

23
00:01:13.700 --> 00:01:18.100
Just be true to yourself until the end

24
00:01:18.230 --> 00:01:22.940
Set sail and grab it, DREAMIN ON

25
00:01:31.900 --> 00:01:39.200
<b>Thunder</b>

26
00:01:45.170 --> 00:01:46.790
Have some more.

27
00:01:46.790 --> 00:01:48.460
Black Maria?

28
00:01:49.510 --> 00:01:53.130
Hey, why aren't you working on your task?

29
00:01:53.130 --> 00:01:55.890
And what task would that be?

30
00:01:55.890 --> 00:01:58.220
The search for my idiot son!

31
00:01:58.220 --> 00:02:02.600
Oh, what's the harm, Viceroy Kaido?

32
00:02:03.100 --> 00:02:06.110
They can handle the search
just fine without me.

33
00:02:06.110 --> 00:02:08.520
I'd rather be here.

34
00:02:10.780 --> 00:02:14.820
Okay, fine! It's that time of year again
to set aside rank and let loose!

35
00:02:14.820 --> 00:02:17.490
Right, Orochi?!

36
00:02:17.490 --> 00:02:18.870
It's an excellent day!

37
00:02:21.620 --> 00:02:23.920
Right you are, Kaido!

38
00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:34.050
The ghosts of the Kozuki Clan that
haunted us for twenty years are finally gone!

39
00:02:34.050 --> 00:02:36.050
It's a day for celebration!

40
00:02:36.050 --> 00:02:39.560
Kanjuro had them all fooled
until the very last minute,

41
00:02:39.560 --> 00:02:44.520
and now his career is complete
after twenty long years!

42
00:02:44.520 --> 00:02:50.780
He'll soon arrive with the captains
who sank the Red Scabbards into the sea!

43
00:02:53.360 --> 00:02:54.950
He's an impressive one!

44
00:02:55.530 --> 00:03:00.700
I could have easily killed him
back then without realizing it.

45
00:03:00.700 --> 00:03:05.210
It's too bad though...
Even after earning all that trust,

46
00:03:05.210 --> 00:03:08.500
Oden never opened up to him.

47
00:03:08.500 --> 00:03:12.760
It's likely those samurai retainers
have not heard anything about it either.

48
00:03:14.010 --> 00:03:15.470
Are you talking about...?

49
00:03:15.470 --> 00:03:17.220
Yeah...

50
00:03:17.220 --> 00:03:23.180
The key to the location of Laugh Tale,
the last island that Roger reached.

51
00:03:27.150 --> 00:03:28.310
Who are you?!

52
00:03:35.360 --> 00:03:37.360
Pardon me!

53
00:03:37.360 --> 00:03:39.320
I have business with Lord Orochi!

54
00:03:39.320 --> 00:03:42.790
Oh! There you are, Kanjuro!

55
00:03:42.790 --> 00:03:44.580
I've never seen him before.

56
00:03:44.580 --> 00:03:46.960
You here for a fight?!

57
00:03:49.330 --> 00:03:51.960
Calm down, you idiots!

58
00:03:51.960 --> 00:03:53.670
He's Orochi's man!

59
00:03:53.670 --> 00:03:56.920
It has been too long, Lord Orochi!

60
00:03:57.590 --> 00:04:01.050
The mansion is so massive that
I got a little lost backstage.

61
00:04:01.050 --> 00:04:01.100
<b>Kurozumi Kanjuro
Shogun Orochi's Informant</b>

