Then how do you explain that haki?!

512
00:24:53.390 --> 00:24:55.850
That hurt!

513
00:25:03.730 --> 00:25:05.650
These guys are amazing...

514
00:25:06.230 --> 00:25:08.110
and there are so many of them.

515
00:25:09.400 --> 00:25:11.240
I was wrong...

516
00:25:12.780 --> 00:25:14.120
to underestimate you.

517
00:25:16.660 --> 00:25:18.910
This castle belongs to an Emperor!

