520
00:25:25.500 --> 00:25:31.090
Shogun Orochi presents
an impromptu special event starting now!

521
00:25:38.310 --> 00:25:39.680
Everyone!

522
00:25:39.680 --> 00:25:42.400
Let me introduce this brat...

523
00:25:46.400 --> 00:25:49.320
Lo and behold...

524
00:25:49.320 --> 00:25:54.320
the son of Kozuki Oden,
